10 REM *** SIMPLE SINGLE-TONE TEST (440 HZ) ***
20 POKE 34864,184 : REM FREQ_LO  (440 = $01B8)
30 POKE 34865,1   : REM FREQ_HI
40 POKE 34868,255 : REM VOLUME (max)
50 POKE 34869,17  : REM CONTROL = $11 = square + gate on
60 PRINT "TONE ON - PRESS A KEY TO STOP"
70 GET K$ : IF K$="" THEN 70
80 POKE 34869,0   : REM gate off = silence
90 END
